Fedora Build steps

1 - base build
2 - Fedora update - sudo dnf update
	sudo dnf install https://download1.rpmfusion.org/free/fedora/rpmfusion-free-release-$(rpm -E %fedora).noarch.rpm
	dnf copr enable erikreider/SwayNotificationCenter
	yum install '*mercurial*'
3 - change desktop manager to SDDM
    sudo dnf install sddm sddm-kcm qt6-qtvirtualkeyboard boost meson ninja-build imv mpd mpc mpv ncmpcpp zsh neovim bat zoxide tmux kitty fzf hyprland dunst qbittorrent waybar gimp shotcut swaybg thunderbird zathura zathura-pdf-mupdf imv SwayNotificationCenter irssi libwayland-devlibgtk-3-dev pkgconf meson gtk3-devel mesa-libgbm-devel nwg-dock
    sudo systemctl disable gdm
    sudo systemctl enable sddm 
    configure sddm (dot file)
    Install themes:
        https://www.pling.com/p/2191680/
 	cp /etc/sddm.conf /etc/sddm/conf/d/sddm.conf
        set theme and enable virtualkeyboard
    Copy to github /etc/sddm.conf.d/sddm.conf
    reboot to test    
Prereqs for Hyprland
    Install MPD - https://www.musicpd.org/download.html
    Install WOFI
    	hg clone https://hg.sr.ht/~scoopta/wofi
	cd wofi
	meson setup build
	ninja -C build
cd ~/Downloads
git clone https://github.com/jblais493/Logos.git



	run hyprland script install to install and configure
5 - Run app deployment script to install apps
